{"schemaVersion":1,"bookId":"situational-15000","unitId":"scene-046","title":"质疑否定","sectionId":"chapter-02","sectionTitle":"日常交际你最强","pageStart":248,"pageEnd":252,"extractionMethod":"text-layer","wordEntryCount":18,"duplicateEntryCount":13,"pages":[{"number":248,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"46 质疑否定"},{"type":"section","text":"Step1 场景词"},{"type":"entry","text":"doubtful [ˈdaʊtfl]","headword":"doubtful"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.可疑的；不能确定的"},{"type":"note","text":"◎be doubtful about对…感到怀疑"},{"type":"entry","text":"sceptical [ˈskeptɪkl]","headword":"sceptical"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.怀疑的；不能确定的（正式用语）"}]},{"number":249,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"irresponsible remarks不负责任的言论","headword":"irresponsible remarks"},{"type":"entry","text":"discredited [dɪsˈkredɪtɪd]","headword":"discredited"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.受到怀疑的；名誉扫地的"},{"type":"note","text":"◎discredited politician名誉扫地的政治家"},{"type":"entry","text":"hard to tell 难说","headword":"hard to tell"},{"type":"entry","text":"scepticism [ˈskeptɪsɪzəm]","headword":"scepticism"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.怀疑主义"},{"type":"entry","text":"question [ˈkwestʃən]","headword":"question"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.问题，疑问；询问；审问"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 询问；审问"},{"type":"note","text":"◎beyond question毫无疑问地"}]},{"number":250,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"raise a question 提出问题","headword":"raise a question"},{"type":"entry","text":"meaningful [ˈmiːnɪŋfl]","headword":"meaningful"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.有意义的"},{"type":"entry","text":"correct [kəˈrekt]","headword":"correct"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.纠正"},{"type":"entry","text":"deny [dɪˈnaɪ]","headword":"deny"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.否认，否定"},{"type":"note","text":"◎deny the truth否认事实"},{"type":"entry","text":"negative [ˈneɡətɪv]","headword":"negative"},{"type":"definition","text":"n./v. 否定"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.负面的"},{"type":"note","text":"◎negative effect负面影响"},{"type":"entry","text":"preliminary objection先决反对，初步异议","headword":"preliminary objection"},{"type":"entry","text":"in the negative 反对的；否定的","headword":"in the negative"},{"type":"entry","text":"never ever 绝不；从不","headword":"never ever"},{"type":"entry","text":"no way 没门","headword":"no way"}]},{"number":251,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"criticism [ˈkrɪtɪsɪzəm]","headword":"criticism"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.批判，批评"},{"type":"entry","text":"lash [læʃ]","headword":"lash"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.猛烈抨击，严厉斥责"},{"type":"section","text":"Step2 学以致用"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 1"},{"type":"example","text":"A：He turned out to be immature and irresponsible.（原来他是个不"},{"type":"text","text":"成熟且不负责任的人。）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：I've told you that at the very start. （我一开始就告诉过你。）"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 2"},{"type":"example","text":"A：You love to play chess, don't you? Come on, there's a whole bunch"},{"type":"text","text":"of friends waiting for you! （你喜欢下象棋吧？来吧，有很多朋友等着"},{"type":"text","text":"你呢！）"}]},{"number":252,"blocks":[{"type":"example","text":"B：All right. I don't deny my passion for chess. By the way, thank you"},{"type":"text","text":"for being there for me. I'm feeling a lot better now. （好吧，我不否认我"},{"type":"text","text":"对象棋的热情。顺便说一句，谢谢你陪在我身边。现在我感觉好多"},{"type":"text","text":"了。）"}]}]}